JAVASCRIPT
(Please tells us what the JavaScript does e.g. "click on the green button and it does the following...")
----------
When the user submits the form:
- If the name field is empty, it shows an alert
- If valid, it changes the form background color based on light/dark mode (green or dark green)
- Displays an alert thanking the user
- Updates the page title with a personalized greeting using DOM manipulation

NOTES TO STAFF
(If there is anything you need to tell us, please use the section below)
---------------
Dark mode styles for form and text are implemented using a `@media (prefers-color-scheme: dark)` block  
JavaScript includes adaptive color response based on system theme  
All requirements are implemented in index.html, style.css, and script.js in the same folder

